SURS

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • SURS.Student

  • public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
    Student class implements methods viewTrascript, addClass, and dropClass. These methods are related to the actions that the student can execute in the system. Student class also contains the constructor to initiate a new Student object.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Marina Chong, Jessica Dozal
